adows]] || '''[[Armando Reynoso|Reynoso]]''' || [[Trevor Hoffman|Hoffman]] (1) || [[Qualcomm Stadium]] || 15,801 || 6&ndash;3 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SDN/SDN200004120.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 10 || April 13 || @ [[2000 San Diego Padres season|Padres]] || 5&ndash;4 || '''[[Brian Anderson (pitcher)|Anderson]]''' || [[Sterling Hitchcock|Hitchcock]] || '''[[Mike Morgan (baseball)|Morgan]]''' (3) || [[Qualcomm Stadium]] || 28,131 || 7&ndash;3 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SDN/SDN200004130.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 11 || April 14 || @ [[2000 San Francisco Giants season|Giants]] || 3&ndash;1 || '''[[Randy Johnson|Johnson]]''' || [[Livan Hernandez|Hernandez]] || ''None'' || [[Pacific Bell Park]] || 40,930 || 8&ndash;3 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SFN/SFN200004140.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 12 || April 15 || @ [[2000 San Francisco Giants season|Giants]] || 7&ndash;4 || '''[[Todd Stottlemyre|Stottlemyre]]''' || [[Russ Ortiz|Ortiz]] || '''[[Greg Swindell]]''' (1) || [[Pacific Bell Park]] || 40,930 || 9&ndash;3 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/SFN/SFN200004150.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 13 || April 17 || [[2000 Colorado Rockies season|Rockies]] || 1&ndash;9 || [[Masato Yoshii|Yoshii]] || '''[[Omar Daal|Daal]]''' || ''None'' || [[Bank One Ballpark]] || 33,743 || 9&ndash;4 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI200004170.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 14 || April 18 || [[2000 Colorado Rockies season|Rockies]] || 7&ndash;1 || '''[[Armando Reynoso|Reynoso]]''' || [[Scott Karl|Karl]] || ''None'' || [[Bank One Ballpark]] || 30,275 || 10&ndash;4 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI200004180.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 15 || April 19 || [[2000 Colorado Rockies season|Rockies]] || 8&ndash;7 || '''