{"title_page": "Frederick Buechner bibliography", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia bibliography}}\nThis is a '''list''' of published works by writer and theologian [[Frederick Buechner]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n80-50015/ |title=Buechner, Frederick: Overview |website=worldcat.org |publisher=WorldCat Identities |access-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007024535/http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n80-50015/ |archive-date=2016-10-07 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.harpercollins.com/author/cr-101130/frederick-buechner/ |title=Frederick Buechner, Author |website=harpercollins.com |publisher=Harper Collins Publishers}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.presbyterianmission.org/story/new-book-celebrates-90-year-legacy-frederick-buechner/ |title=New book celebrates 90-year legacy of Frederick Buechner |website=presbyterianmission.org |publisher=Presbyterian Mission |access-date=2018-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205171227/http://www.presbyterianmission.org/story/new-book-celebrates-90-year-legacy-frederick-buechner/ |archive-date=2017-02-05 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n== Nonfiction ==\n* ''The Magnificent Defeat'', 1966 ({{ISBN|9780060611743}})\n* ''The Hungering Dark'', 1968 ({{ISBN|9780060611750}})\n* ''The Alphabet of Grace'', 1970 ({{ISBN|9780060611798}})\n* ''Wishful Thinking: A Seeker's ABC'', 1973 ({{ISBN|9780060611392}})\n* ''Faces of Jesus: A Life Story'', 1974 ({{ISBN|9781612615905}})\n* ''Telling the Truth: The Gospel As Tragedy, Comedy, and Fairy Tale'', 1977 ({{ISBN|9780060611569}})\n* ''Peculiar Treasures: A Biblical Who's Who'', 1979 ({{ISBN|9780060611415}})\n* ''The Sacred Journey: A Memoir of Early Days'', 1982 ({{ISBN|9780060611835}})\n* ''Now and Then: A Memoir of Vocation'', 1983 ({{ISBN|9780060611828}})\n* ''A Room Called Remember'', 1984 ({{ISBN|9780060611859}})\n* ''Whistling in the Dark: A Doubter's Dictionary'', 1988 ({{IS